data.description: Welcome to the gorgeous neighborhood of Pecos Manor! This home offers 5 bedrooms, 2.5 baths and 9-foot ceilings. Kitchen features oak cabinetry with 42-inch uppers, island and SS appliances. Kitchen flows seamlessly into the family room with sliding door to back patio. Primary with ensuite has a charming Juliet balcony, double sinks, separate shower & soaker tub and a huge walk-in closet. You'll love the covered patio with synthetic grass and a hot tub to relax. This property has solar panels that are paid off! No high electric costs here. 14 SEER AC, BIB R21 wall insulation & R38 at ceiling, low E dual paned windows, programmable thermostats, post tension foundation and the Energy Star label. Minutes to school, shopping and restaurants.
